{"tid":1314902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[童軍器材編]超市五金可入手—盡快睇","createTime":"2019-07-14T11:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T12:07:39.000Z","uid":35776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2dff6bafd3b420cee86aad26660ef45924e5fbe0","tid":1314902,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:18:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>投射器</strong><br />\nA 金屬湯殼&mdash;超市可入手，不銹鋼更佳<br />\n用法:同狗一樣放慣用手嘅肩上，勺位可以放到拳頭大小物品，配合臂展投射距離更遠，較硬同重嘅可作防身器具<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ikea.cn/cn/zh/images/products/grunka-ge-lun-ka-tang-shao__0718978_PE731808_S4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ikea.cn%2Fcn%2Fzh%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fgrunka-ge-lun-ka-tang-shao__0718978_PE731808_S4.JPG&h=76830005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nB 自拍棍+膠紙+膠樽<br />\n剪開膠樽兜位上半部份，加膠紙固定落自拍棍 <br />\n⚠注意：耐久較低<br />\n<br />\nC 皮帶+膠紙+膠兜<br />\n<br />\nB嘅變種，皮帶優點多用途，可隨時變形做其他版本<br />\n<br />\n打住遠程先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954ef85338d4830ec9b7da5e965cac8b3389e5bf","tid":1314902,"uid":35776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:39:20.000Z","msg":"<strong>軟硬式打狗棒</strong><br />\n<br />\n野外多野狗，防身有辦法<br />\n<br />\nA 皮帶+任意硬身直條(1ft)<br />\n<br />\n用兩條膠條夾住皮帶冇扣一端，用膠紙or索帶固定形成手柄就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n⚠ 使用其間避免傷及其他童軍<br />\n用法類同&darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QfU8BxiZ9Os\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQfU8BxiZ9Os&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPah3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=b9c59d5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QfU8BxiZ9Os</a><br />\n<br />\nB 硬物+繩+硬條<br />\n<br />\n原理一樣<br />\n<br />\n⚠ 大鎖頭is gd<br />\n<br />\n<strong>伸縮OO</strong><br />\n<br />\n驗樓神器 睇樓必備<br />\n<br />\n<strong>防狗水</strong><br />\n<br />\n園藝噴壺(小)：2m 至 4m<br />\n加壓噴壺(大)：&gt;5m 有待測試<br />\n<br />\nothers：包書膠 長遮 行山竹 <del>牧童笛</del>"},{"pid":"0cec53a6176f6b329ea2260a3d6da325d7fb442f","tid":1314902,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:07:39.000Z","msg":"樓上街坊可用湯殼加射程"}]}